h5pactivity.name: Learning Check 1
h5pactivity.intro: Now that you are midway through this course, you will have an opportunity to gauge and reinforce what you’ve learned. Once finished, select the link titled "Unit 3: Building and Sustaining Employer Partnerships" at the bottom to move on.
